snippet.title: AMG DAO Gameplay Series - Soccerverse
snippet.description:
JOIN THE ELITE!
Introducing Soccerverse.  A multiplayer, community-driven football management simulator and trading game.
Real Stakes
A paradigm shift in gaming where
you not only compete for fun against other players but also earn real value.
Provably Fair
Cheating is a thing of the past. All actions are transparent and all
the code is opensource.
Decentralised
A game universe that runs unstoppable, censorship resistant, trustless and autonomous. Fully on-chain.

You can find more information about what are we doing and how you can find us:
https://linktr.ee/joinamg
